            "summaryHtml": "<ul>\n<li>This paper by Szegedy et al. from Google in AAAI 2017 introduced the latest versions of the Inception model – <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1602.07261\">InceptionV4</a> and <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1602.07261\">Inception-ResNet</a>.</li>\n</ul>"
